description:
This is a 11 minute workout called '10 min STANDING ARM WORKOUT | With Dumbbells | Biceps, Triceps and Shoulders | Zero Pushups' from the channel fitbymik.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Join me for a 10 min STANDING ARM WORKOUT to sculpt and strengthen your upper body. All you need is a medium set of dumbbells. I'll be using 8 lb weights, but choose the weight that best suits your strength level. Each interval will be 45 seconds on and 15 seconds rest. This is an ALL STANDING wrist friendly workout, with zero planks or pushups! So grab your weights and let's get ready to feel the burn! ðŸ’ž xox Mik
